Class SecretShare.SplitSecretOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tiemens.secretshare.engine.SecretShare.SplitSecretOutput
  • Enclosing class:
    SecretShare

    public static class SecretShare.SplitSecretOutput
extends java.lang.Object
    When the secret is split, this is the information that is returned. Note: This object is NOT the "public" information, since the polynomial used in splitting the secret is in this object. The "public" information is the '.getShareInfos()' method.
